The same process is applied to all the child nodes in the arrival punctuality model (i.e. “ACC”, “PCC”, “TC”, “MISC”, “MPC”, “VC”, “UE”, “PC”, “VOP” and “SPEED”). The number of pieces of data that need to be transformed and inserted into the arrival punctuality model is 259 per expert.
